
http://lau.linuxaudio.org/TiMidity-howto.html

install timidity


make sure alsa volume is on


check to see timitidy is installed, running  & find the timitidty virtual midi prots 
	jcran@disko:~$ aconnect -i -o
		[snip]
	client 128: 'TiMidity' [type=user]
	    0 'TiMidity port 0 '
	    1 'TiMidity port 1 '
	    2 'TiMidity port 2 '
	    3 'TiMidity port 3 '

find raw midi device

	jcran@disko:~$ aconnect -i
		
		[snip]

	client 129: 'Client-129' [type=user]
	    0 'Virtual RawMIDI '


connect alsa out to timiitiy
	    
	jcran@disko:~$ aconnect 129:0 128:0 


ruby 1.8.7
gem install 'midiator'
@midi = MIDIator::Interface.new
@midi.autodetect_driver
@midi.play( 84, 0.5 )


